room_title: Escape room "Airlock Escape" by Escape Room Zone in Detroit
room_address: 1490 N Oakland Blvd, Waterford Twp, MI 48327
room_description: You’ve been abducted to an alien space station! NASA is aware of the situation but can not help you. Those that have been abducted before you have left clues to help you but it is up to you to find your way through the space station and find the escape pod. It’s your only hope for returning to Earth if you can find it before the aliens arrive to take you away!
